ay Undead Skill</span><hr size=1> Additional question...<br>Does Dex effect the chance to get your cleansing crit. I have US 1 and not seeing very many cleanses at all.<br>Thanks, <p>Winterz The Impatient Grammarian<BR>Built Horde Tough<BR>"I don't pull trains, I pull experience"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhakashakamalakabalsaka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Haka Shakamalakabalsaka</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 256<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/23/02 12:07:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=71.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Slay Undead Skill</span><hr size=1> One question I have is if it's worth to get Slay Undead if you have a low damage weapon... I'm assuming the ratio of damage would be near the same, and besides the coolness factor of doing more damage than a double backstab in one hit, is there any reason that a Pally should not get Slay Undead if they plan on using a lower dmg weapon? <p>Haka Shakamalakabalsaka <br>Level 56 Holy Knight<br>Asatru <br><br>Hanka <br>Level 21 Enchanter <br>Aventyre Krigare <br><br>Povar <br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyandroszzyzzx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yandros Zzyzzx</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 71<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/25/02 10:45:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=71.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Slay Undead Skill</span><hr size=1> So does the maximum hit possible with SU3 turn out to be 100X your base weapon damage? <br><br>I'm really looking forward to getting this skill even though I'm still working on CF2. :(<br><br>Yandros <p> <img src=http://eagle.clarion.edu/~faculty/johns/Yandros5.jpg></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uyandroszzyzzx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yandros Zzyzzx</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0> at: 3/27/02 4:41:57 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiustus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iustus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 627<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/27/02 6:50:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=71.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Slay Undead Skill</span><hr size=1> yes, it seems to be just under 100 x base weapon damage.<br><br>-Iustus <p><BR><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=124361>Duke Iustus</a><BR>Crusader of Marr <BR>Tarew Marr<BR><BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ueanaddare.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eanaddare</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/28/02 10:01:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=71.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ne.jp/asahi/robin/zander/eq/chara03ett.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Slay Undead Skill</span><hr size=1> ac of the mob will be taken into account.<br><br>